             was indicted for <rs id="t18130217-85-off501" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18130217-85-off501" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130217-85-off501" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18130217-85-cd502" type="crimeDate">20th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130217-85-off501 t18130217-85-cd502"></join>, six dozen of saw-files, value 16 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18130217-85-victim815" type="victimName">
                     David 
                     Courley
                  <interp inst="t18130217-85-victim815" type="surname" value="Courley"></interp>
